{"tid":451442,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"依隻雀ge媾女方法完全同毒撚追女冇分別","createTime":"2017-10-29T08:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T11:31:39.000Z","uid":84481,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"97327a1a25be360aabb289ace59088111095c728","tid":451442,"uid":84481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T08:29:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1XkPeN3AWIE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1XkPeN3AWIE&d=jyirg4QFkV9BO7jd8cClNY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5ca1feea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1XkPeN3AWIE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nD毒撚一有女埋身就即刻夠衝show off自己d柒技<br />\n但同時又唔夠膽直視女神<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/161929_12092556a4bc3bf7ff9974de259aa739.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F161929_12092556a4bc3bf7ff9974de259aa739.jpg&h=4482ad03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/162414_bf8391f71000ae2213003cbaba7f0ba1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F162414_bf8391f71000ae2213003cbaba7f0ba1.jpg&h=a85e1e9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞左咁耐又成機掂下條女<br />\n女神都冇走到就開始ff以為自己得米啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/162019_a305d53d2382626e2b30d1457804f5cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F162019_a305d53d2382626e2b30d1457804f5cb.jpg&h=098e4c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知臨門一腳總會比mk仔飛埋黎一野搶走條女<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/161237_4ddb903f12a71dbf8c3bd35343126dfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F161237_4ddb903f12a71dbf8c3bd35343126dfc.jpg&h=45e26230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSometimes whatever you do, things just don&rsquo;t work out <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/161312_a8cde616c5bf13f01d5799403c390985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F161312_a8cde616c5bf13f01d5799403c390985.jpg&h=2370bad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我屌鳩你地啊死mk仔臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依隻雀ge媾女同毒撚追女一樣咁撚柒同廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f52fda8ffedc93ce541f7fd4a910789c199432","tid":451442,"uid":84481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a33022acfe893408ba85c57669feb4307460021","tid":451442,"uid":85280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T10:19:41.000Z","msg":"Ron and Becky"},{"pid":"6c0ee4d60ed2e717908b71660a85ba37aaf4139a","tid":451442,"uid":129039,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T10:20:48.000Z","msg":"圓丁鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b1a6dd96fe05338f8615583f8806c92c84dda6","tid":451442,"uid":55016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ron and Becky</blockquote><br />\nLemme smash"},{"pid":"bf5a514da0d81d27d5c23261fee75fbeb76a6741","tid":451442,"uid":129039,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"做乜負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495afbc76518a38c52349d38671d50f0d985e6bc","tid":451442,"uid":55732,"